==================================================
Assignment 1 — Task List CRUD Application
==================================================

Objective:
Build a Task Management application where users can manage daily tasks.

Task Object Structure:
- id
- title
- description
- status (Pending / Completed)
- priority (Low / Medium / High)
- createdAt

Functional Requirements:
1. Create Task
2. Read Tasks
3. Update Task
4. Delete Task
5. Mark Complete
6. Search & Filter
7. Sorting
8. Local Storage Integration

Desired Output:
- Total Tasks
- Completed Tasks
- Pending Tasks
- Task listing UI